title: Anniversary Icon ??
body: i still don't have it riot please

replies.body:
*Zombiemaster* is correct. We've had to send these gifts out in waves due to just how many we're sending out.

Let me know if you don't have anything by the 23rd please.
I still haven't gotten them either and I've been playing for the past several months. 0_e

We're still getting content sent out, and as *Zombiemaster* mentioned, the deadline looks to be the 30th now.

Let me know if you have any other questions.
I too don't have any gifts. I don't have the Kayle skin OR the icon, and I have definitely been present for the match requirements.
The gifts are not done being distributed. The final day is the 23rd, so if you don't have it by then, you can submit a support ticket.
The skins are still being distributed, and the final date has been pushed back to the 30th, as per the banner on the [support page](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us).
I've already received the Kayle and Kayle skin but I haven't gotten the icon yet please send it to me.
